        section.details
            section#products.details-section
                .row
                    .col.span_3_of_3
                        h2.services-header Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) System
                .row
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            img.services-img(src="img/users.svg")
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            h5.services-subheader HRMS & Payroll
                            span.horizontal-line
                            p Our HRMS & Payroll system provides functionalities and easy to use features to manage the human reasources in any organization starting from employee on-boarding to final settlement.
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            img.services-img(src="img/tools.svg")
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            h5.services-subheader Inventory
                            span.horizontal-line
                            p Our Inventry system provides functionalities to track inventory levels, orders, sales and delivery. 
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            img.services-img(src="img/credit.svg")
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            h5.services-subheader Accounting
                            span.horizontal-line
                            p Our Accounting system provides functionalities to collect, store, process and report financial data.
            section.feature-section
                .row
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        ul
                            li.feature Access/Refresh token based authentication
                            li.feature SSL/TLS Support (HTTPS)
                            li.feature Scalability with multiple nodes
                            li.feature On-premise or cloud deployment (Upcoming release)
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        ul
                            li.feature Employee document management
                            li.feature Employee profile image management
                            li.feature Permanent salary components management
                            li.feature Optional benefits management
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        ul
                            li.feature Configurable employee attributes (Upcoming release)
                            li.feature Payslip generation & viewimg
                            li.feature Leave management
                            li.feature User level access control
            section.details-section
                .row
                    .col.span_3_of_3
                        h2.services-header Salesforce Management System
                .row
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            img.services-img(src="img/man.svg")
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            h5.services-subheader Salesforce Management System
                            span.horizontal-line
                            p Our Salesforce Management System enables an organization to track the sales process from lead generation to the actual sales.
                    .col.span_2_of_3
                        .col.span_3_of_3
                            img.filler-laptop(src="img/placeit.png")
            section
                .filler-image
            section#services.details-section
                .row
                    .col.span_3_of_3
                        h2.services-header Other Services
                .row
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            img.services-img(src="img/tablet-mobile-combo.svg")
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            h5.services-subheader Cloud & App Development
                            span.horizontal-line
                            p We develop mobile apps hosted from cloud to provide all time availability and scalability.
                    .col.span_1_of_3
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            img.services-img(src="img/iconmonstr-computer-9.svg")
                        .col.span_1_of_2
                            h5.services-subheader Other Services
                            span.horizontal-line
                            p We have decade long experience in developing software applications to solve business problems. We have an experienced team of professionals that uses the latest technologies and best practices to deliver custom applications.
